==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: yī zhāo bèi shé yǎo, shí nián pà jǐng shéng 

===Etymology===
Literally: Bitten by a snake on one morning, afraid of the rope by the well for ten years.

===Proverb===
'''[[一]][[朝]][[被]][[蛇]][[咬]]，[[十]][[年]][[怕]][[井]][[繩]]'''

# [[once bitten, twice shy]].

===Alternate forms===
[[一朝被蛇咬，十年怕井绳]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

===Related terms===
*[[一]][[朝]][[被]][[蛇]][[咬]]，[[十]][[年]][[怕]][[草]][[绳]]

